description:
Michael Rapaport is not only an incredibly talented and respected actor...he's also adorably insane! Listen in as Anna and Michael go "toe-to toe" in their first meeting and discuss how Wikipedia pages can negatively affect lives, why women who know how to dive into swimming pools are sexier and how reality TV is similar to the UFC. In a hilarious exchange, Anna also refuses to let Michael live down the STD he may or may not have contracted back in high school! You'll also hear them role-play a bar "pick-up" scene and share a crazy story about a woman Michael dated who slept with two very high profile athletes from the same team. (You'll have to listen to find out who!) The gang also helps callers dealing with threesome etiquette and "bro-code."

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
